text:
For anyone that finds this: I ended up creating a new page and adding the modules one by one and, sure enough, there was a single module that was causing the whole issue.

Looking through, it was a fairly innocuous issue (referencing an undeclared variable), but it managed to impact all the modules on page. My guess is that hsDebug allowed execution to continue when it otherwise wouldn't have, causing it to work under hsDebug, but not normally.
Can someone please help me to list data FROM custom object using hubl and set pagination and filter also? Need pagination without page refresh
